trigger for main and release branches\n42:   - Purpose: Trigger on PR to main/release branches\n43:   - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n44:   - Verification: `grep \"pull_request:\" .github/workflows/main.yml && grep \"main\" .github/workflows/main.yml`\n45: \n46: - [ ] **T2.4**: Add `on: push` trigger for main branch\n47:   - Purpose: Trigger on push to main\n48:   - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n49:   - Verification: `grep \"push:\" .github/workflows/main.yml`\n50: \n51: - [ ] **T2.5**: Define `build` job with `runs-on: ubuntu-latest`\n52:   - Purpose: Set runner environment\n53:   - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n54:   - Verification: `grep \"runs-on: ubuntu-latest\" .github/workflows/main.yml`\n55: \n56: - [ ] **T2.6**: Add `actions/checkout@v4` step\n57:   - Purpose: Checkout repository code\n58:   - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n59:   - Verification: `grep \"uses: actions/checkout@v4\" .github/workflows/main.yml`\n60: \n61: - [ ] **T2.7**: Add `docker/setup-buildx-action@v3` step\n62:   - Purpose: Configure Docker Buildx\n63:   - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n64:   - Verification: `grep \"uses: docker/setup-buildx-action@v3\" .github/workflows/main.yml`\n65: \n66: - [ ] **T2.8**: Add `make docker-build` step\n67:   - Purpose: Build workloadmanager Docker image\n68:   - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n69:   - Verification: `grep \"make docker-build\" .github/workflows/main.yml`\n70: \n71: ### Phase 3: lint.yml - Go Lint with Path Filter (ST-3)\n72: \n73: - [ ] **T3.1**: Create workflow file `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n74:   - Purpose: Initialize lint workflow file\n75:   - File: `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n76:   - Verification: `test -f .github/workflows/lint.yml`\n77: \n78: - [ ] **T3.2**: Add workflow name \"Go Lint\"\n79:   - Purpose: Define workflow display name\n80:   - File: `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n81:   - Verification: `grep \"name: Go Lint\" .github/workflows/lint.yml`\n82: \n83: - [ ] **T3.3**: Add `on: pull_req