{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775890911894,"sessionID":"ses_284aaac7fffeHSsO4kjDxi3Fdq","part":{"id":"prt_d7b58d0f50010Gcwiesdjei8Av","messageID":"msg_d7b55e93b0019D6ft60YG3RZxu","sessionID":"ses_284aaac7fffeHSsO4kjDxi3Fdq","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-d51778fa00b0443c8267d3344949014c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-035/tasks.md","content":"# AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成 |\n| Module | `client-go` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Codegen Script Update (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Update `hack/update-codegen.sh` to use k8s.io/code-generator v0.34.1\n  - Purpose: Use correct code-generator version for client generation\n  - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n  - Verification: `grep \"k8s.io/code-generator\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2**: Add input-base parameter pointing to pkg/apis\n  - Purpose: Specify API source directory for code-generator\n  - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n  - Verification: `grep \"input-base\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n\n- [ ] **T1.3**: Add clientset-path parameter for clientset output\n  - Purpose: Generate clientset in client-go/clientset/versioned/\n  - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n  - Verification: `grep \"clientset-path\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n\n- [ ] **T1.4**: Add informer-path parameter for informers output\n  - Purpose: Generate informers in client-go/informers/externalversions/\n  - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n  - Verification: `grep \"informer-path\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n\n- [ ] **T1.5**: Add lister-path parameter for listers output\n  - Purpose: Generate listers in client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/\n  - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n  - Verification: `grep \"lister-path\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\