st, err := lister.AgentRuntimes(\"my-ns\").List(labels.Everything())\n\n// Get specific resource\nar, err := lister.AgentRuntimes(\"my-ns\").Get(\"my-agentruntime\")\n```\n\n### Fake Clientset Usage Pattern\n\n```go\nfakeClient := fake.NewSimpleClientset(\n    &runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n        ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"test-ar\", Namespace: \"default\"},\n    },\n)\n\n// Test CRUD operations\nar, err := fakeClient.RuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Get(ctx, \"test-ar\", metav1.GetOptions{})\n```\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: Codegen Script | T1.1-T1.8 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 2: Boilerplate | T2.1-T2.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 3: Directory Structure | T3.1-T3.7 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 4: Generate Clientset | T4.1-T4.10 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 5: Typed Clients | T5.1-T5.16 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 6: Fake Clients | T6.1-T6.6 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 7: Informer Factory | T7.1-T7.10 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 8: Generic Routing | T8.1-T8.6 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 9: Runtime Informers | T9.1-T9.14 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 10: Listers | T10.1-T10.11 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 11: Doc Files | T11.1-T11.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 12: File Count | T12.1-T12.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 13: Go Build | T13.1-T13.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 14: Integration | T14.1-T14.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 15: Routing Test | T15.1-T15.2 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 16: Unit Tests | T16.1-T16.5 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 17: Makefile | T17.1-T17.3 | Pending | 0% |\n\n**Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/119 tasks)**\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Design: `changes/AR-035/design.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-035/delta-spec.md`\n- Proposal: `changes/AR-035/proposal.md`\n- Spec: `changes/AR-035/spec.md`\n- Root Delta Spec: `delta-spec.md`\n- Makefile: `Makefile`\n- Codegen Script: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n- k8s.io/code-generator: https://github.com/kubernetes/co